name: Janet
description: I don’t know if there is any other person in this world with a burning desire to live, to learn everything new, to share (even my little experiences) with others. I am very sociable, joyful, open-hearted and frank person. I like to communicate with people, to foresee their thoughts and opinions; I feel myself comfortable and good in the crowd. I am also very helpful and careful girl, I always put aside my things if some of my friends needs help or care
